flowchart TD
    Length[Telomere Length] <--> TRF1Calc{n_TRF1 = L / 18}
    TRF1Calc -->|n_TRF1 < 400| OpenGate[Gate OPEN<br/>Extension Allowed]
    TRF1Calc -->|n_TRF1 ≥ 400| ClosedGate[Gate CLOSED<br/>Extension = 0 EXACT]
    OpenGate --> Extension[Add Repeats + POT1 5×]
    Extension --> HardCap[Clip at 7200 bp]
    HardCap --> Length
    ClosedGate --> Length
    style ClosedGate fill:#f44336
    style OpenGate fill:#4caf50